        -:  184:      *
        -:  185:      * In the case of a compile-time column 1D array, implicit transposition from a single row is allowed.
        -:  186:      * Therefore <code> Array<int,Dynamic,1>{{1,2,3,4,5}}</code> is legal and the more verbose syntax
        -:  187:      * <code>Array<int,Dynamic,1>{{1},{2},{3},{4},{5}}</code> can be avoided:
        -:  188:      *
